data.description: Let me introduce you to "The Vincent"! Check out this new construction ranch style home just minutes away from all that Downtown Durham has to offer. Step into this absolutely stunning floor plan that features an open concept layout. Perfect for entertaining! Granite countertops lay atop your beautiful cabinets along with a huge center island! The high ceilings and natural lighting adds a more spacious feel to the home! Come and check it out!
